text: Yhlas Magtymov (20 April 1992) is a Turkmen professional footballer who plays for Şagadam FK and Turkmenistan as midfielder. == Club career == At 2019 season signed a contract with Şagadam FK. ==International career== He played for Turkmenistan youth team in Commonwealth of Independent States Cup 2012. Magtymov made his senior national team debut on 8 August 2016, in friendly match against Oman national football team. == Honours == ==References== ==External links== * *Player Info Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Turkmenistan footballers Category:Turkmenistan international footballers Category:Association football midfielders
